Monopoly.LoggerTools

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • Monopoly.LoggerTools.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
    The Logger class allows for the creation and storing of logs, along with displaying logs during runtime and post-runtime.
